<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>msẖ bạhwn ʿlyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 msẖ bạhwn ʿlyk tsybny fy ạlkẖṭạyạ

[V2]
 trtẖy lḍʿfy yạ yswʿ wkmạn tsẖfʿ fy

[V3]
 fạtḥ ạ̹ydk ly wḥḍwrk ymlạny

[V4]
 wbḥb tqwl ly ạ̹nk lsh bạqy ʿly

[V5]
 tʿạla yạ yswʿ bktny wgẖyrny

[V6]
 ạ̉nạ bạṣdq ạ̹n ʿlạjy ʿndk wḥdk

[V7]
 mạ fy gẖyrk ạ̉nạ ṭạlbh wqlby mstny

[V8]
 ạ̉ʿml fy wgẖyr qlby ʿlsẖạn mjdk

[V9]
 msẖ bạhwn ʿlyk tsybny fy qywdy

[V10]
 tyjy bnwrk wbḥnạn wtksẖf ạ̉srạry

[V11]
 msẖ ʿlsẖạn tksrny lkn jạy tsẖfyny

[V12]
 qạblny wmạ fy sẖyʾ ʿnk mdạry

[V13]
 klmny bklạm ạlḥq wạlḥryẗ

[V14]
 fk qywdy wgẖyr qlby wgẖyr ḥạly

[V15]
 mạ fy gẖyrk hyqwm nfsy ạlmḥnyẗ

[V16]
 ly ḥryẗ wnṣrẗ bạldm ạlgẖạly</lyrics>
<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<hymn_number>9741</hymn_number>
</song>